Class AnimalsTest

java.lang.Object
model.AnimalsTest
class AnimalsTest extends Object
Unit tests for the Animals class. This class uses JUnit 5 to test various behaviors of the Animals class, including its properties and methods. Each test method verifies one aspect of the Animals class. This follows standard unit test conventions and aims to ensure correctness in core functionalities.
Version:
3.0
Author:
Justin, Fatema, Manveet
